          "reviewBody": "I’m so glad I chose Sanskruti School for my child. The environment is nurturing, and the teachers go above and beyond to ensure every student feels confident and supported. The facilities are excellent, and the school encourages overall development through sports, arts, and academics. Highly satisfied!",
