            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "A great school.for CBSE pattern. This school focuses on making kids understand rather than mugging up. This school has four campuses in Pune. The teachers are very good and keep track of kids growth in each aspect. This school has numerous extra curricular activities like swimming, horse riding, indoor games, skating etc. All games don't need any additional charges. These are part of the school fee. The school fee is much lower than the other reputed schools. Fee has defined percentage of increase in 3 year band. Abrupt fee structure change is not done here.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
