          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am writing to express my serious concerns regarding the careless driving behavior exhibited by the driver of the school bus that transports our children to and from school.\n\nToday, around 3:30 PM near LMD Chowk, I experienced a very alarming incident. As I was seated on my scooty, the school bus made a U-turn around the chowk in a reckless manner. This sudden and unsafe maneuver caused a near collision with my vehicle. My 5-year-old daughter, who was with me, was extremely frightened by the incident, and I narrowly escaped what could have been a severe accident.\n\nSuch driving behavior is not only dangerous but also unacceptable, especially considering the precious lives the driver is responsible for every day. The safety of our children should be the utmost priority, and I urge you to take immediate action to address this issue.\n\nI kindly request that you investigate this matter and ensure that the driver receives the necessary guidance and training to prevent such incidents in the future. Additionally, please consider implementing stricter monitoring of driving practices to ensure the safety of all students.",
